research_municipality_step.notes: Seagraves, TX operates under a General Law Type A government, which is a form of mayor-council system. The list of officials is compiled from multiple sources, with some potential overlap or changes in individuals with similar names (e.g., Debra Lerma, Lee Lerma, Debra Middleton). All listed individuals are identified as elected officials or hold roles typically filled by elected council members. Specific district information was only consistently available for Ruben Valles.
